div.div:
Earth in the 21st century has fused with another world. An era of “dungeons” teeming with monsters, the “adventurers” that raid them, and the most elite educational facility in South Korea that fosters these adventurers: “Warrior High School.”
Although he was once considered the greatest adventurers in Asia, he has been accused with false chargers and, while dungeon smuggling in order to pay for his sick father’s medical treatments, Yoo Jaryong comes across a teen.
“You there, get in Warrior High School.”
This is a story about a young man who’s lost his dream and hiding his identity finding himself once again.
(Source: KakaoPage, translated)

The Yakmun clan, which boasted a long time ago, was wiped out in a massacre. The corpses piled up like mountains, and the blood flooded everything like ocean water. Amidst this hell of despair, Sura, opened his eyes: "No one shall be spared. I shall kill everyone. It doesn't end unless I've killed each and every one of them."
Jin Ja-Kang was the lone survivor, and with him a man's lonely revenge, which will be recorded as a legend in the Murimsa Temple in the future, begins!
(Source: KakaoPage, translated)
